ption><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 01:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-resists-examining-its-own-failures-another-war-awaits-us/0000018b-b066-df42-a78f-bd67ae6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理助手寻求机密材料，以免除内塔尼亚胡对 10 月 7 日袭击事件的责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/aide-to-israels-pm-seeks-classified-material-to-absolve-netanyahu-of-blame-for-oct-7/0000018b-b089-d3c1-a39b-bee9dfa10000</link><description>所要求的信息，包括之前内阁会议的记录，因违反政府法规而被禁止共享</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 23:55:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/aide-to-israels-pm-seeks-classified-material-to-absolve-netanyahu-of-blame-for-oct-7/0000018b-b089-d3c1-a39b-bee9dfa10000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德挫败真主党针对巴西犹太人的袭击计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-thwarts-attack-planned-by-hezbollah-against-jews-in-brazil/0000018b-b0fd-dea2-a9bf-f0ff37c20000</link><description>两名巴西公民因策划代表恐怖组织袭击犹太人而被捕。圣保罗拉比表示，自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，犹太社区处于“高度戒备”状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 23:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-thwarts-attack-planned-by-hezbollah-against-jews-in-brazil/0000018b-b0fd-dea2-a9bf-f0ff37c20000</guid></item><item><title>杀害底特律犹太教堂主席萨曼莎·沃尔的嫌疑人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/suspect-arrested-in-killing-of-detroit-synagogue-president-samantha-woll/0000018b-b0a6-df42-a78f-bde765470000</link><description>40 岁的萨曼莎·沃尔 (Samantha Woll) 上个月被发现死在家外。周三，底特律警方宣布逮捕一名嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 20:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/suspect-arrested-in-killing-of-detroit-synagogue-president-samantha-woll/0000018b-b0a6-df42-a78f-bde765470000</guid></item><item><title>英国的犹太学生在一个月内面临“一年多的反犹太事件”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/jewish-students-in-the-u-k-face-over-a-years-worth-of-antisemitic-incidents-in-a-month/0000018b-aff0-dedf-adab-eff04f440000</link><description>该组织表示，面对辱骂、恐吓和死亡威胁，犹太学生已向犹太学生联盟的福利热线拨打了 400 多个电话</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 19:37:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/jewish-students-in-the-u-k-face-over-a-years-worth-of-antisemitic-incidents-in-a-month/0000018b-aff0-dedf-adab-eff04f440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的 TROPHY 系统如何在加沙保护坦克免受反坦克火力攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-trophy-system-protects-tanks-from-anti-tank-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</link><description>在哈马斯的视频中，以色列坦克被反坦克火箭击中，但在许多情况下，它们实际上表明旨在拦截威胁的技术正在发挥作用</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 19:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-trophy-system-protects-tanks-from-anti-tank-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不应该上映展示哈马斯暴行的电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-08/ty-article/.highlight/why-israel-shouldnt-release-the-film-showing-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-b019-d3c1-a39b-bef9b4930000</link><description>哈马斯大屠杀的视觉证据并不缺乏。但有无数的历史、政治和心理原因让人们观看它并看到与以色列人期望的完全不同的东西</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 19:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-08/ty-article/.highlight/why-israel-shouldnt-release-the-film-showing-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-b019-d3c1-a39b-bef9b4930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方收集哈马斯袭击期间轮奸的目击者证词</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/israeli-police-collect-eyewitness-testimony-of-gang-rape-during-hamas-attack/0000018b-b025-d3c1-a39b-bee5ef400000</link><description>警方调查人员一直在收集哈马斯恐怖分子在 10 月 7 日袭击期间实施性侵犯和性虐待行为的目击者的证词。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/israeli-police-collect-eyewitness-testimony-of-gang-rape-during-hamas-attack/0000018b-b025-d3c1-a39b-bee5ef400000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击一周年之际，家人讲述了痛苦、失落和对政府的愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/marking-one-month-to-hamas-attack-families-speak-of-pain-loss-and-anger-at-government/0000018b-afbc-d3c1-a39b-bffdb5240000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列为遇难者举行哀悼日，遇难者家属聚集在特拉维夫悼念亲​​人。其中一位承诺：那些对这场灾难负责的人“将回家、入狱或下地狱”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:32:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/marking-one-month-to-hamas-attack-families-speak-of-pain-loss-and-anger-at-government/0000018b-afbc-d3c1-a39b-bffdb5240000</guid></item><item><title>帮助经历 10 月 7 日袭击事件、遭受创伤的以色列儿童再次成为孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/helping-traumatized-israeli-children-who-experienced-the-october-7-attack-be-kids-again/0000018b-afe7-dea2-a9bf-ffffdfe70000</link><description>以色列救生联合会的成员每周都会举办几次游戏，帮助孩子们重建恢复能力。创始人保罗·哈基姆 (Paul Hakim) 解释说：“我们让大脑告诉身体一切都好。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/helping-traumatized-israeli-children-who-experienced-the-october-7-attack-be-kids-again/0000018b-afe7-dea2-a9bf-ffffdfe70000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争爆发一个月后，以色列正在经历一个超越政治的时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/one-month-into-gaza-war-israel-is-experiencing-a-moment-that-transcends-politics/0000018b-afbe-d3c1-a39b-bfff853a0000</link><description>极端正统派男子正在为军队签名，阿拉伯以色列人正在与犹太以色列人一起帮助流离失所者。但不要过于乐观——自 10 月 7 日以来，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和他的顽固支持者并没有改变</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 17:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/one-month-into-gaza-war-israel-is-experiencing-a-moment-that-transcends-politics/0000018b-afbe-d3c1-a39b-bfff853a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府将接受私人捐款资助加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-will-accept-private-donations-to-fund-war-in-gaza/0000018b-af50-dea2-a9bf-ffde12340000</link><description>批评者表示，该指令为外部对政府优先事项的不当影响和对普通公民的剥削打开了大门</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-will-accept-private-donations-to-fund-war-in-gaza/0000018b-af50-dea2-a9bf-ffde12340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列扣留资金帮助战争撤离人员的真正原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/the-real-reason-israel-is-holding-up-money-to-help-war-evacuees/0000018b-af8d-df42-a78f-afcfabe10000</link><description>没有钱请正统派老师吗？那么以色列战争撤离者也没有钱：以色列政府试图淡化这个等式</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:25:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/the-real-reason-israel-is-holding-up-money-to-help-war-evacuees/0000018b-af8d-df42-a78f-afcfabe10000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔的认罪笔录在他发动的战争中重新审视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-confession-transcript-reexamined-amid-a-war-he-started/0000018b-af64-dea2-a9bf-fffe1c080000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙对哈马斯发动战争，有关哈马斯领导人和 10 月 7 日建筑师叶海亚·辛瓦尔 (Yahya Sinwar) 的记忆被重新唤起，他曾因谋杀罪在以色列服无期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-confession-transcript-reexamined-amid-a-war-he-started/0000018b-af64-dea2-a9bf-fffe1c080000</guid></item><item><title>“即使在伦敦也很可怕”：六名以色列人逃离该国开始新生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-here-in-london-its-scary-what-being-an-israeli-abroad-now-is-like/0000018b-ae87-df42-a78f-afc7cf810000</link><description>奥里特（Orit）是一位导乐师，虽然身在佐治亚州，但仍在帮助她的老客户生孩子；安德烈（Andrey）对他所看到的视频感到震惊；亚登（Yarden）正在勇敢地面对伦敦喧闹的抗议活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-here-in-london-its-scary-what-being-an-israeli-abroad-now-is-like/0000018b-ae87-df42-a78f-afc7cf810000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列内塔尼亚胡仍然向普京和俄罗斯卑躬屈膝？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-is-israels-netanyahu-still-groveling-to-putin-and-russia/0000018b-af21-dea2-a9bf-ffbf3e0c0000</link><description>十年来，以色列一直急于安抚莫斯科。但内塔尼亚胡坦率地对莫斯科采取令人尴尬的绥靖政策并没有带来明显的收获。相反，在 10 月 7 日的暴行发生后，普京立即加强了与伊朗的合作并接待了哈马斯领导人</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-is-israels-netanyahu-still-groveling-to-putin-and-russia/0000018b-af21-dea2-a9bf-ffbf3e0c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列模特被选为迪奥广告大片后，亲巴勒斯坦活动人士呼吁抵制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-activists-call-for-boycott-after-israeli-model-is-chosen-for-dior-campaign/0000018b-af36-dea2-a9bf-ffbe3be30000</link><description>这家著名的法国时装公司邀请以色列人 May Tager 参与圣诞广告活动，引发了社交媒体上大量愤怒的帖子。 “迪奥选择凶手是为了他们的竞选活动，现在一切都散发着血腥味”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:01:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-activists-call-for-boycott-after-israeli-model-is-chosen-for-dior-campaign/0000018b-af36-dea2-a9bf-ffbe3be30000</guid></item></channel></rss>